<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">它長長的尾巴真是酷啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算變成了化石，<delay8 />依然栩栩如生，<delay20 />
看起來就好像<delay8 />隨時都會動起來呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是說，它的角還真雄偉呢！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算頭頂上<delay8 />長了這麼大的角，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真虧它還能<delay8 />好好保持平衡啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它就算變成化石，<delay8 />一樣還是很有魄力呢！<delay40 />
一想到這傢伙以前都是在天上飛，<delay20 />
光是想像，<delay8 />我就覺得好興奮啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它明明是化石，<delay20 />卻散發出驚人的威嚴感啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不愧是暴龍，<delay8 />真是太帥氣了，<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難怪它會被稱作最強的恐龍呢。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">它背上的鋸齒，<delay8 />看起來真有型呢！<delay40 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過它竟然都用這麼龐大的身體行走，<delay20 />
對我來說，<delay8 />完全無法想像啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它的脖子這麼長，<delay20 />簡直就像長頸鹿呢！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是有這麼長的身高，<delay20 />
就能輕鬆眺望遠處，<delay8 />感覺很方便啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">長毛象呢，<delay8 />雖然身體很巨大，<delay20 />
但它的牙齒<delay8 />也很引人注目呢！<delay40 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是跟它單挑，<delay8 />我實在贏不了啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得這生物的形狀<delay8 />還真複雜耶！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且它的體型也滿大的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />害我以為是外星人的化石哩。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然化石<delay8 />就是有種浪漫感啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它看起來<delay8 />雖然像隻普通的魚，<delay20 />
不過真正的它<delay8 />不知道是什麼樣子！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">沒想到它就算變成化石，還是這麼嚇人，<delay20 />
這傢伙<delay8 />真不是普通的壞人臉呢！<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />它看上去就很強，<delay8 />我很喜歡喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Silent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過啊，<delay8 />風神翼龍……<delay20 />
好像不太能用力踏步耶！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />腳跟腰果然還是很重要哩！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">什麼東西？<delay frames="30" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />咦！<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />竟然連這種東西都變成了化石，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Angry" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是一點都大意不得啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />沒想到這麼小隻的生物<delay8 />
竟然跟恐龍們生活在同一個時代<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真是令人敬佩啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說這個化石<delay8 />是你捐贈的啊！<delay40 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我能夠像這樣<delay8 />悠閒地欣賞化石，<delay20 />
也都多虧了你耶！<delay8 />謝謝你喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="201" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哇～<delay20 />這真是太驚人了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />進化的歷史<delay8 />原來是這種感覺啊！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />總覺得有點感動了呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>